Event & Kickball & Picnic & Softball \\ \hline 
& & &\\[-1.5ex]
Fraction liking event & $\frac{11}{30}$ & $\frac{7}{20}$ & $\frac{5}{12}$ \\[1ex] \hline
\end{tabular}
inference:

$\frac{11}{30} > \frac{7}{20} > \frac{5}{12}$ 
Converting to the same denominator: $60>42>30$ 
Hence, from most popular to least popular: Kickball, Picnic, Softball 

Final Answer: \boxed{Kickball, Picnic, Softball. I hope it is correct.}
